com.independentsoft.exchange
Enum UserSettingName

java.lang.Object
  java.lang.Enum<UserSettingName>
      com.independentsoft.exchange.UserSettingName
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<UserSettingName>
public enum UserSettingName
extends java.lang.Enum<UserSettingName>

Identifies the user settings to be returned in an Autodiscovery. These settings are the settings that can be requested using the GetUserSettings method. Identifies the user settings.
